OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784378874
OL,3,CIllegal schools are 'scourge on
OL,4,Csociety' warns Ofsted boss
OL,6,FIllegal schools are a "scourge on
OL,7,Fsociety" and more will be done to
OL,8,Fprosecute offenders, Ofsted's chief
OL,9,Finspector Sir Martyn Oliver has
OL,10,Fpledged, following an ITV News
OL,11,Finvestigation exposing the scale of
OL,12,Fthe issue.
OL,14,FLast month ITV News found some pupils
OL,15,Facross England are being taught in
OL,16,Fdangerous, filthy conditions, by
OL,17,Funqualified staff, and identified 20
OL,18,Fsuspected illegal schools in England.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784378874
OL,3,CIllegal schools are 'scourge on
OL,4,Csociety' warns Ofsted boss
OL,6,FSir Martyn expressed his concerns
OL,7,Fabout children getting a "narrow or
OL,8,Fwholly inappropriate curriculum" in
OL,9,Fthese settings, which may damage their
OL,10,Flife chances.
OL,12,F"It could be about conspiracy theories
OL,13,For extremist teachings taking place,
OL,14,Fall sorts of not good provision," he
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,FBy law, anywhere providing full-time
OL,18,Feducation, defined as 18 hours or more
OL,19,Fa week, to five or more kids must
OL,20,Fregister as a school and be inspected.
OL,26,@tD@AOUvD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
