CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784378874
OL,3,CIllegal schools are 'scourge on
OL,4,Csociety' warns Ofsted boss
OL,6,FHowever, many don't and instead go
OL,7,Funder the radar.
OL,9,FOthers use loopholes in the legal
OL,10,Fdefinition of a school, claiming that
OL,11,Fthey operate only for a limited number
OL,12,Fof hours to evade oversight.
OL,14,FSir Martyn admitted Ofsted doesn't
OL,15,Fknow the full scale of the problem
OL,16,Fbecause many of these establishments
OL,17,Fare hidden by their very nature.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
