OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784378874
OL,3,CIllegal schools are 'scourge on
OL,4,Csociety' warns Ofsted boss
OL,6,FIf you want to share your experience
OL,7,Fof illegal or unregulated schools, you
OL,8,Fcan get in touch with Sarah Corker and
OL,9,Fthe team by emailing:
OL,10,Fsocialaffairs@itv.com
OL,12,FA conservative estimate is that 6,500
OL,13,Fchildren are in illegal schools across
OL,14,FEngland, but the true figure is likely
OL,15,Fto be much higher.
OL,17,FThere have only been nine prosecutions
OL,18,Fsince Ofsted's illegal schools team
OL,19,Fwas established more than a decade ago.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784378874
OL,3,CIllegal schools are 'scourge on
OL,4,Csociety' warns Ofsted boss
OL,6,FReferencing the current legal
OL,7,Fdifficulties facing his inspectors in
OL,8,Fentering these premises and seizing
OL,9,Fevidence, Sir Martyn told ITV News:
OL,10,F"We've had one hand tied behind our
OL,11,Fback for the last 12 years doing this
OL,12,Fwork."
OL,14,FHe said under the new Children's
OL,15,FWellbeing and Schools Act, Ofsted will
OL,16,Fhave more powers to "start to tackle
OL,17,Fsome of those settings and to shine a
OL,18,Flight on them once and for all".
OL,26,@rD@AOUtD@FO]xD@UOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784378874
OL,3,CIllegal schools are 'scourge on
OL,4,Csociety' warns Ofsted boss
OL,6,FThe new legislation, which received
OL,7,Froyal assent earlier this year, will
OL,8,Fgive Ofsted stronger powers to search
OL,9,Fand seize evidence, something the
OL,10,Fregulator can't currently do.
OL,12,FInspectors will also have the ability
OL,13,Fto question witnesses on site, and
OL,14,Fapply a warrant when settings block
OL,15,Faccess.
OL,17,FCouncils will have to keep a register
OL,18,Fof home-schooled children, helping to
OL,19,Ffind those in illegal settings.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784378874
OL,3,CIllegal schools are 'scourge on
OL,4,Csociety' warns Ofsted boss
OL,6,FThe Act will also tighten the
OL,7,Fdefinition of a school to prevent
OL,8,Fsettings from exploiting loopholes.
OL,10,FIt will include any institution which
OL,11,Fprovides the majority of a child's
OL,12,Feducation during the school day, no
OL,13,Fmatter how narrow the curriculum is.
OL,15,FHowever, many of the measures won't
OL,16,Fcome into force until Autumn 2027 at
OL,17,Fthe earliest, and many require
OL,18,Fsecondary legislation, something which
OL,19,Fthe Ofsted boss described as a source
OL,20,Fof "frustration" for his team.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
