OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784378874
OL,3,CIllegal schools are 'scourge on
OL,4,Csociety' warns Ofsted boss
OL,6,FExperts have warned that thousands of
OL,7,Fchildren are being hidden away in
OL,8,Fsuspected illegal or unregistered
OL,9,Fschools, labelled "breeding grounds
OL,10,Ffor extremism", and receiving a
OL,11,Fsubstandard education.
OL,13,FITV News has spoken to dozens of
OL,14,Fformer students and whistleblowers
OL,15,Ffrom across the country who were all
OL,16,Fcritical of the segregated education
OL,17,Fthey received.
OL,19,FThere have been 1,839 Ofsted
OL,20,Finvestigations into suspected illegal
OL,21,Fschools over the last decade.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784378874
OL,3,CIllegal schools are 'scourge on
OL,4,Csociety' warns Ofsted boss
OL,6,FThe highest number is in London, with
OL,7,F335 investigations, and in Yorkshire,
OL,8,Fwhere there have been 266.
OL,10,FOf those inspected, almost a fifth
OL,11,Fwere religious schools and
OL,12,Fpredominantly Christian, Jewish and
OL,13,FMuslim.
OL,15,FThose found running an illegal school
OL,16,Fcan face up to six months in prison,
OL,17,Fan unlimited fine, or both.
OL,19,FVictor Shafiee headed up Ofsted's
OL,20,Fillegal schools team for a decade
OL,21,Fbefore retiring earlier this year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784378874
OL,3,CIllegal schools are 'scourge on
OL,4,Csociety' warns Ofsted boss
OL,6,FHe warned the issue had been
OL,7,F"deprioritised" under regulator's
OL,8,Fcurrent leadership and added that he
OL,9,Fthought Ofsted didn't have the
OL,10,Fresources needed.
OL,12,F"Year on year the budget for this work
OL,13,Funder the new chief inspector has been
OL,14,Fcut," he said.
OL,16,F"I fear children being radicalised, I
OL,17,Ffear children's lives being destroyed."
OL,26,@tD@AOUxD@AOUyD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784378874
OL,3,CIllegal schools are 'scourge on
OL,4,Csociety' warns Ofsted boss
OL,6,FResponding to that criticism, Sir
OL,7,FMartyn pointed to what he said are the
OL,8,Ffirst "set of powers in Ofsted's
OL,9,Fhistory to do more to prosecute and to
OL,10,Fobtain warrants", something the
OL,11,Fregulator has been lobbying for for
OL,12,Fmany years.
OL,14,FHe strongly refuted that budgets had
OL,15,Fbeen cut, in fact arguing the very
OL,16,Fopposite.
OL,26,@rD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784378874
OL,3,CIllegal schools are 'scourge on
OL,4,Csociety' warns Ofsted boss
OL,6,F"The illegal schools team has more
OL,7,Fmoney and more staff than ever before
OL,8,Fand is part of a national team. We are
OL,9,Fdetermined to use these new powers to
OL,10,Fdrive the scourge of illegal schools
OL,11,Fout of our country," he said.
OL,13,FIt's not just the dangerous learning
OL,14,Fconditions that inspectors are worried
OL,15,Fabout, but dangerous people too.
OL,17,FMany sites do not do criminal records
OL,18,Fchecks on staff, some of whom have no
OL,19,Fbackground in teaching.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
