OL,3,CIllegal schools are 'scourge on
OL,4,Csociety' warns Ofsted boss
OL,6,FDame Rachel De Souza, Children's
OL,7,FCommissioner for England, described
OL,8,Fthe conditions revealed in our
OL,9,Finvestigation as "disgusting," adding
OL,10,Fthat children shouldn't be "spending
OL,11,Fone minute there, let alone their
OL,12,Fentire education."
OL,14,FShe said: "The safeguarding issue
OL,15,Foutweighs everything.
OL,26,@vD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30814
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784378874
OL,3,CIllegal schools are 'scourge on
OL,4,Csociety' warns Ofsted boss
OL,6,F"It should be a top priority for the
OL,7,Fregulator, for government to make sure
OL,8,Fwe know where every child is, that
OL,9,Fthey're receiving a decent education
OL,10,Fand that they're safe. It's that
OL,11,Fsimple."
OL,13,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@sD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
