OL,3,CIllegal schools are 'scourge on
OL,4,Csociety' warns Ofsted boss
OL,6,FA Department for Education
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "We will not
OL,8,Ftolerate settings operating illegally
OL,9,Fas unregistered schools, putting
OL,10,Fchildren's futures at risk."
OL,12,F"That's why through the Children's
OL,13,FWellbeing and Schools Act we are
OL,14,Fstrengthening Ofsted's powers to
OL,15,Finvestigate suspected unregistered
OL,16,Fschools.
OL,26,@oD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/16
