OL,3,CIllegal schools are 'scourge on
OL,4,Csociety' warns Ofsted boss
OL,6,F"These measures will help ensure
OL,7,Fvulnerable children are not hidden
OL,8,Ffrom services, attend safe educational
OL,9,Fsettings and receive the education
OL,10,Fthey deserve."
